OL,3,CMetrolink strikes called off after
OL,4,Cworkers secure new pay deal
OL,6,FStrike action on Manchester's
OL,7,FMetrolink tram system has been called
OL,8,Foff after the Unite union struck a new
OL,9,Fpay deal with the employer.
OL,11,FProposed strikes due to take place
OL,12,Flater this week will not take place
OL,13,Fdue to hundreds of workers being set
OL,14,Fto receive a substantial pay rise.
