OL,3,CMetrolink strikes called off after
OL,4,Cworkers secure new pay deal
OL,6,FThe Unite union says customer service
OL,7,Frepresentatives at the bottom of the
OL,8,Fpay scales will see a minimum pay
OL,9,Fincrease of 14 per cent over the next
OL,10,Fthree years and those at the top of
OL,11,Ftheir pay scales will receive a
OL,12,Fminimum of nine per cent.
OL,14,FDrivers will see a minimum of a nine
OL,15,Fper cent increase over the same period
OL,16,Falongside a substantial reduction of
OL,17,Fthe pay progression scale.
