OL,3,CMetrolink strikes called off after
OL,4,Cworkers secure new pay deal
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a hard fought and well
OL,8,Fdeserved pay award for Metrolink's
OL,9,Fworkers.
OL,11,F"The initial pay deal was well short
OL,12,Fof their expectations and by standing
OL,13,Ftogether as a union, and with the
OL,14,Fthreat of strike action in the mind of
OL,15,Fthe employer, they have negotiated a
OL,16,Fvastly improved deal."
OL,18,FUnite regional officer Colin Hayden
OL,19,Fadded: "Metrolink had sought to short
OL,20,Fchange our members and undervalue
OL,21,Ftheir hard work and skill.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
