OL,3,CMetrolink strikes called off after
OL,4,Cworkers secure new pay deal
OL,6,F"Through tough negotiations and by
OL,7,Fbeing prepared to walkout they have
OL,8,Fsecured a new pay deal that will put
OL,9,Fthousands in their pockets over the
OL,10,Fnext three years. This demonstrated
OL,11,Fthe financial value in joining a
OL,12,Funion."
OL,14,FDamien Chabas, Managing Director of
OL,15,FKeolis Amey Metrolink said: "We
OL,16,Fremained committed to meaningful
OL,17,Fdiscussion with Unite throughout these
OL,18,Fpay talks to ensure we could agree a
OL,19,Ffair pay deal for all our employees.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
