OL,3,CMetrolink strikes called off after
OL,4,Cworkers secure new pay deal
OL,6,F"This three-year deal provides all
OL,7,Femployees with a substantial pay
OL,8,Fincrease, protects against
OL,9,Finflationary increases and addresses
OL,10,Fhistorical pay progression concerns.
OL,12,F"We are pleased customers will not be
OL,13,Fimpacted and Metrolink will run in
OL,14,Fline with the scheduled timetable."
